Changes to adapt new AITER MoE API;
Changes to adapt new AITER MLA API (MTP is not enabled)
Some other bug fixes;
This PR is for AITER API changes introduced by commit 939f741fc37f46694e48c32c7164f49eae2584c4 (merged on 04/20/2025). AITER versions after this require this patch to work.

This change adds a Content-Type: application/json header to /ping and /health as per #17036. I've also changed the test_openai_schema.py to remove an await that caused the following failure:
    @schema.parametrize()
    @schema.override(headers={"Content-Type": "application/json"})
    async def te
